# Intuition
In this type of questions, we need to think what is happening at every index and what is repeating.
At every index we need to find whether in left their is decreasing and in right there is increasing or not.
So instead of calculating every time we store the length of decreasing and increasing in 2 auxilliary array, and using this 2 array as lookup to find which index is safe.
