# Approach: 2 vectors(prefix and suff), one to store the number of days before the ith day that is non-increasing, and another array to store the number of days after the ith day that is non-decreasing.

<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->

# Complexity
- Time complexity: O(n)
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

- Space complexity: 3O(n)
